Rating: 4
This recipe was a surprising hit! Even the teenagers like it. Some of my Easter guests had salt and sugar dietary restrictions, so finding something that everyone could eat and would like was tricky. I left the salt out of the marinade, but everyone loved it and had seconds! My dad craves salt but can't have any and the vinegar in the recipe seemed to do the trick for him.

