This is a great party dish because it must be made one day ahead except for the final dressing and it makes a beautiful presentation. I first served it for Easter with a fresh ham. Then I served it again for a baby shower luncheon. My one addition was to sprinkle crumbled feta cheese between the vegetables right before serving.